<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The socks are in pairs.</li>
      <li>There are 12 socks.</li>
      <li>You could count by 2 to find the total number of socks.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>How many socks are there?</li>
      <li>How many pairs of socks are there?</li>
      <li>Why are there 6 pairs of socks?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


